item.description: From the time you turn onto 106, you will go through 4 sets of lights before you need to take the 1st left.   Come on over to my place on Sat. March 24th @ 6:30pm for appetizers, a movie, good conversation and lots of laughs. I enjoy making chili and I can pick up a few quesadillas from Chipotle. Feel free to bring along your favorite appetizer or dessert. Once you rsvp, please email me for my address.
item.name: APPETIZER AND MOVIE NIGHT - SAT. MARCH 24TH - 6:30 PM
